	<h1 class="title">就算在流媒体曝光过，Drake 的专辑依然成为今年首张白金唱片</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">刘平安 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-14 15:00:19 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13534/medium/13534.jpg?1439531285" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13534" data-title="《就算在流媒体曝光过，Drake 的专辑依然成为今年首张白金唱片》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13534/medium/13534.jpg?1439531285" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13534" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
